summary:
Senior project manager / project director for international water supply projects. Manager of the water supply business unit at Witteveen+Bos with a group of 35 professionals working on leading edge technology projects in the Netherlands, Ghana, Indonesia, Kazakhstan and other countries.

Specialties: Project management and international business development in water supply.

Honorary Consul for Fiji (in the Netherlands): connecting Fiji and NL, and favoring the interests of Fiji.
